{"title": "How to Add room to an appointment?", "body": "This article will cover how to add a room to an appointment.\nClick New Appointment from the appointment book top Right or click the Time-slot to open the appointment form.\n\nSelect the Patient Name from the list or create a new one.\nClick the drop-down to reveal the room list and select the room\nComplete the appointment form with all the required details\nClick Save to complete\nClick here to learn how to move patients back and forth from the Waiting Room section to the With Provider section of the Waiting Room page"}